java.io.Serializable
public class Designer
extends RationaleElement
implements java.io.Serializable

The Designer refers to the person who entered some element of the rationale although it could also be used to refer to who is responsible. This was added for the ORCA extensions and needs more work to be complete.

burgeje

Constant Field Values

corpPosition

java.lang.String corpPosition
The designer's position within the corporation. This probably should be changed to refer to the CorpPosType but is just a string for now.

projPosition

java.lang.String projPosition
The designer's position/role on the project. This is different from corporation position - for example, a senior engineer might be a team leader or they could be a product designer, or...

How much experience does the designer have at their current job (would position make more sense?)
